                        <interp inst="t18480703-name-188" type="surname" value="GILLETT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480703-name-188" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>SAMUEL GILLETT</persName>
                  </hi>. I was looking at the horse—I saw Nixon with the handkerchief in his band.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Nixon's Defence.</hi> I met this boy; I saw the horse lying down, and this handkerchief was lying down; I took it up, and Goodman said. "Don't take it, for fear you should be caught for thieving;" and I put it down again.</p>
